{"tid":1108013,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[入場支持高質港產] 最新香港電影討論區 (3)","createTime":"2019-04-15T15:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T02:53:28.000Z","uid":15213,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d3251d4c8b020ec91096890ec1d424625d1e1f6d","tid":1108013,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"金像獎已完滿結束<br />\n要繼續推介大家入場睇好嘅港產片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要畀人知港產唔再只係警匪 唔只係商業大作 唔只係古天樂劉青雲<br />\n一樣有似《淪落人》呢種感動人心的小品<br />\n黃秋生話呢啲片種難搵投資所以先唔收片酬拍<br />\n但總唔可以個個唔收錢<br />\n所以如果有好戲係應該買返張飛支持一下本地影業<br />\n支持新導演新演員<br />\n令佢哋更多機會拍更好作品給觀眾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我開呢個post就係盡量分享同討論新港產片<br />\n希望觀眾能夠揀到適合自己的電影入場～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2cdc085d67d10ce40bc1bbd70e90941f6e929a","tid":1108013,"uid":15213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"上映中：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wmoov.com/assets/movie/photo/201903/HO00000566_1551870523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fassets%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201903%2FHO00000566_1551870523.jpg&h=45516805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淪落人 (Still Human)</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">榮獲3項金像獎：</span></strong></span> <br />\n最佳男主角 <strong>黃秋生</strong><br />\n最佳新晉導演 <strong>陳小娟 </strong><br />\n最佳新演員 <strong>Crisel Consunji </strong>"},{"pid":"34d9cdecdc0c49f77e74749426faa67decceaeb9","tid":1108013,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a